column2: SELECT TOP # m.name, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, n.specObjID, n.distance, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.z, s.zErr, s.zWarning, s.class, s.subclass, s.ra AS ra2, s.dec AS dec2 into mydb.MyTable from MyDB.wise_scosmos AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS s ON n.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE s.z IS NOT #
